											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Moving still: Stelmane and Emperor toasting one another in her office. &#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;The Emperor pulls out the chair for her. She sits. Shot of her in her big chair with her eyes rolled to the whites, completely posssessed. &#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;NB this is the same as the scene in INT_EmperorRevealed_AfterOrpheus but with the added reveal of Stelmane's possession. " />
